<br>
This is a long read, but well worth the time. The original post can be viewed <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub8.ezboard.com/faoopguildcharacternews.showMessage?topicID=41.topic">here</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->.<br>
